{"tid":2231946,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"點解大家要杯葛學校入面既大陸仔？","createTime":"2020-10-06T04:57:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T13:50:44.000Z","uid":112551,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"44efa194d5c2569c09282416eacfe05c1672a1c5","tid":2231946,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T04:57:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5qs761g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5qs761g.png&h=b438b1c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沒有看過相關教材 須符合大眾需求、人民的要求<br />\n家長耿先生從內地來港十多年，小朋友就讀小一。他表示，教師沒有遵從正規的教材是應該被取消（教師）資格，但他沒有看過相關教材，只是從電台、電視得悉事件，「符合大眾需求、人民的要求，心態要端正，不然孩子會出現各種各樣的問題。」作為家長的他，未來會多留意功課，「每天都看一看，問一問」，過去他從沒想到學校會出「這麼大的問題，如果再發現問題，肯定會投訴。」<br />\n<br />\n支那種邊有得教化 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40533fa8604beb578dc0cf0cff196f16b197d8b5","tid":2231946,"uid":41545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T13:10:46.000Z","msg":"返大陸啦 落黎香港做乜柒姐<br />\n落到黎仲撚低賤過係上面<br />\nBtw姓耿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"111e28aa464abf7511536f1017ecebff337e66af","tid":2231946,"uid":286155,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T13:26:28.000Z","msg":"杯鬼杯馬咩<br />\ne家啲小學生個撚個講普通話架喇"},{"pid":"418574f7718c9d735a9b9db53c93a6a7b649f73b","tid":2231946,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"111e28aa464abf7511536f1017ecebff337e66af","tid":2231946,"uid":286155,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T13:26:28.000Z","msg":"杯鬼杯馬咩<br />\ne家啲小學生個撚個講普通話架喇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T13:29:21.000Z","msg":"大家生多啲仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔夠人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成班都係支那仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6369e9ac5083e5a00c0a65ee31ea4a